with our partners nationally. In order to protect the integrity of the criminal investigation, Kelowna RCMP are unable to provide specific details with respect to the investigation at this time." ' || CHR(13) || CHR(10) || CHR(13) || CHR(10) || '  The crane collapse at a downtown Kelowna highrise construction site claimed the lives of four construction workers - Cailen Vilness, Erick and Patrick Stemmer and Jared Zook - along with Brad Zawislak who was killed inside a neighbouring building where he was working.
