 || 'A high streamflow advisory has been issued for the Thompson River downstream of Kamloops Lake, and high streamflow advisories remain in effect for the Similkameen and Nicola.' || CHR(13) || CHR(10) || CHR(13) || CHR(10) || 'The Ministry of Forests says convective precipitation is expected to continue Monday, with 15-25 mm precipitation possible through the region. "The upcoming weather pattern is similar to thunderstorms that caused flooding on Mission Creek near Kelowna in June 2022."' || CHR(13) || CHR(10) || CHR(13) || CHR(10) || 'Environment Canada issued a special weather statement on Sunday, indicating that heavy rainfall is expected on Tuesday over much of the North Thompson, South Thompson and Bonaparte River watersheds. It''s forecasting rainfall totals from 20-40 mm, with higher amounts on east-facing mountain slopes.','Wet weather triggers new flood watches and high streamflow advisories','Internet',1,1,0,null,to_date('22-MAY-23','DD-MON-RR'),to_date('22-MAY-23','DD-MON-RR'),null,null,null,'column','Castanet','Castanet',null,null,'SyndEnclosureImpl.length=66442' || CHR(13) || CHR(10) || 'SyndEnclosureImpl.interface=interface com.sun.syndication.feed.synd.SyndEnclosure' || CHR(13) || CHR(10) || 'SyndEnclosureImpl.type=image/jpeg' || CHR(13) || CHR(10) || 'SyndEnclosureImpl.url=https://www.castanet.net/content/2023/5/screen_shot_2023-05-22_at_8.56.14_am_p3688601.jpg',0,0,null,to_date('01-JAN-70','DD-MON-RR'),null,null,'https://www.castanet.net/news/Kelowna/427997/Wet-weather-triggers-new-flood-watches-and-high-streamflow-advisories',0,null,0,0,null,0,0,0,0,'tday',0,0,0,null,0,0,0,0,null,null,null);
