t. John, but firefighters say changing wind directions and cooler weather have helped temper those blazes so far this weekend. [forr, embc, pssg, maz]','New wildfire in BC''s central Interior sparks evacuation order in parts of Cariboo','CP News',1,1,0,null,to_date('21-MAY-23','DD-MON-RR'),to_date('21-MAY-23','DD-MON-RR'),null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,0,0,null,to_date('01-JAN-70','DD-MON-RR'),null,null,'http://www.commandnews.com/fpweb/fp.dll/$bc-rss/htm/rss/x_dv.htm/_ibyx/daj/_svc/cp_pub/_Id/2107944970/_k/6IGPhTksQQjJSQpV',0,null,0,0,null,0,0,0,0,'calmazan',0,0,0,null,0,0,0,0,null,null,null);
