ered Saturday near Griffon Ridge is also under control.' || CHR(13) || CHR(10) || CHR(13) || CHR(10) || 'West of Sun Peaks, a spot fire discovered Friday, east of Louis Creek, has been brought under control. It''s believed to be human caused.' || CHR(13) || CHR(10) || CHR(13) || CHR(10) || 'South of Barnhartvale, a lightning strike spot fire near Campbell Creek is also under control.' || CHR(13) || CHR(10) || CHR(13) || CHR(10) || 'Meanwhile, after reports of smoke near Armstrong Friday, a spot fire was located near the section of the Grey Canal Trail east of Swan Lake.' || CHR(13) || CHR(10) || CHR(13) || CHR(10) || 'It''s believed to be human caused, but was brought under control. [forr, embc, pssg, env]','Lightning strikes bring several spot fires across Thompson-Okanagan ','Internet',1,1,0,null,to_date('22-MAY-23','DD-MON-RR'),to_date('22-MAY-23','DD-MON-RR'),null,null,null,'column','Castanet','Castanet',null,null,'SyndEnclosureImpl.length=67477' || CHR(13) || CHR(10) || 'SyndEnclosureImpl.interface=interface com.sun.syndication.feed.synd.SyndEnclosure' || CHR(13) || CHR(10) || 'SyndEnclosureImpl.type=image/jpeg' || CHR(13) || CHR(10) || 'SyndEnclosureImpl.url=https://www.castanet.net/content/2023/5/screen_shot_2023-05-22_at_7.20.29_am_p3688590.jpg',0,0,null,to_date('01-JAN-70','DD-MON-RR'),null,null,'https://www.castanet.net/news/BC/427988/Lightning-strikes-bring-several-spot-fires-across-Thompson-Okanagan',0,null,0,0,null,0,0,0,0,'artapia',0,0,0,null,0,0,0,0,null,null,null);
