y safety related projects throughout B.C. through six funding streams that align with government commitments in various priority areas related to public safety. [pssg, mcfd, hlth, zpz]','Vernon-Monashee MLA announces $150,000 for Archway Society for Domestic Peace','Internet',1,1,0,null,to_date('20-MAY-23','DD-MON-RR'),to_date('20-MAY-23','DD-MON-RR'),null,null,null,'column','Castanet','Castanet',null,null,'SyndEnclosureImpl.length=49367' || CHR(13) || CHR(10) || 'SyndEnclosureImpl.interface=interface com.sun.syndication.feed.synd.SyndEnclosure' || CHR(13) || CHR(10) || 'SyndEnclosureImpl.type=image/jpeg' || CHR(13) || CHR(10) || 'SyndEnclosureImpl.url=https://www.castanet.net/content/2023/5/screen_shot_2021-03-31_at_2.44.56_pm_p3521630_p3688190.jpg',0,0,null,to_date('01-JAN-70','DD-MON-RR'),null,null,'https://www.castanet.net/news/Vernon/427738/Vernon-Monashee-MLA-announces-150-000-for-Archway-Society-for-Domestic-Peace',0,null,1,0,null,0,0,0,0,'calmazan',0,0,0,null,0,0,0,0,null,null,null);
