and advised people to keep out and stay back from the river bank.' || CHR(13) || CHR(10) || CHR(13) || CHR(10) || '"This is not the time to be on the river," Swanson said. "Even though it''s hot right now and looks inviting, it is very fast and it''s very cold."' || CHR(13) || CHR(10) || CHR(13) || CHR(10) || 'Floating on the river is a common summer activity, when water flow is much slower and the water is warmer, Swanson said.','Family rescued from Puntledge River after trying to flat during high flows','Newspaper',0,1,0,null,to_date('14-MAY-23','DD-MON-RR'),to_date('14-MAY-23','DD-MON-RR'),null,null,'A03','column','Roxanne Egan-Elliott','Roxanne Egan-Elliott',null,null,null,0,0,null,to_date('01-JAN-70','DD-MON-RR'),null,null,null,0,'krypto',0,0,null,0,0,0,0,'calmazan',0,1,0,null,0,0,0,0,null,null,null);
