ut urging the province to do more to get vapes out of the hands of kids sooner. ' || CHR(13) || CHR(10) || CHR(13) || CHR(10) || 'The Surrey school district is considering joining other school districts like New Westminster in installing surveillance cameras and putting vape detectors in bathrooms. ' || CHR(13) || CHR(10) || CHR(13) || CHR(10) || 'Matthew says they are planning to have the pilot project at one school, but Kailay wants more actions. [zhj, hlth, edu]','Bhullar/Kailey/Matthew/Bhurji/Lam  - school vaping concerns','TV News',0,1,0,null,to_date('25-MAY-23','DD-MON-RR'),to_date('25-MAY-23','DD-MON-RR'),null,null,null,'column','OMNI Punjabi News','OMNI Punjabi News',null,null,null,0,2400,null,to_date('01-JAN-70','DD-MON-RR'),'779298329.mp4','2023/05/24/779298329.mp4',null,0,'krypto',0,0,'video/quicktime',1,0,1,0,'asidhu',0,0,0,null,0,0,0,0,'Teen vaping','Issues','2023-05-25');
