ould operate in Winnipeg, Moose Jaw, Sask., and Portage la Prairie, Man., if it wins the bid. [tran, pssg]','Kelowna''s KF Aerospace part of multi-billion-dollar contract bid to train RCAF','Internet',1,1,0,null,to_date('15-MAY-23','DD-MON-RR'),to_date('15-MAY-23','DD-MON-RR'),null,null,null,'column','Castanet','Castanet',null,null,'SyndEnclosureImpl.length=69115' || CHR(13) || CHR(10) || 'SyndEnclosureImpl.interface=interface com.sun.syndication.feed.synd.SyndEnclosure' || CHR(13) || CHR(10) || 'SyndEnclosureImpl.type=image/jpeg' || CHR(13) || CHR(10) || 'SyndEnclosureImpl.url=https://www.castanet.net/content/2023/5/skyalyne-plane._p3685964.jpg',0,0,null,to_date('01-JAN-70','DD-MON-RR'),null,null,'https://www.castanet.net/news/Kelowna/426623/Kelowna-s-KF-Aerospace-part-of-multi-billion-dollar-contract-bid-to-train-RCAF',0,null,0,0,null,0,0,0,0,'jglass',0,0,0,null,0,0,0,0,null,null,null);
