 CHR(13) || CHR(10) || CHR(13) || CHR(10) || 'Police say a suspect fled in a silver or grey four-door sedan. Police have not said if any arrests have been made.' || CHR(13) || CHR(10) || CHR(13) || CHR(10) || 'About 20 minutes after the shooting, police responded to a vehicle fire in the area of Cape Horn Avenue and United Boulevard in Coquitlam. Investigators said they believe the shooting and the fire are related.' || CHR(13) || CHR(10) || CHR(13) || CHR(10) || 'Police are asking anyone who may have witnessed this incident or saw a silver or grey coloured four-door sedan in the area of David Avenue and Coast Meridian Road or Cape Horn Avenue and United Boulevard in Coquitlam to contact investigators.' || CHR(13) || CHR(10) || CHR(13) || CHR(10) || 'The force is also looking for dashcam or cellphone video from the area or surrounding streets and alleyways of where the shooting or vehicle fire took place between 7:15 p.m. and 8:15 p.m. Wednesday.' || CHR(13) || CHR(10) || CHR(13) || CHR(10) || 'Coquitlam RCMP can be contacted at 604-945-1550 with the file number 2023-12269. [pssg]','Man suffers life-threatening injuries in targeted shooting in busy area of Coquitlam: police','Internet',1,1,0,null,to_date('18-MAY-23','DD-MON-RR'),to_date('18-MAY-23','DD-MON-RR'),null,null,null,'SyndCategoryImpl.taxonomyUri=null SyndCategoryImpl.name=News/Canada/British Columbia ','CBC Online','CBC Online',null,null,null,0,0,null,to_date('01-JAN-70','DD-MON-RR'),null,null,'https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/british-columbia/coquitlam-shooting-david-avenue-coast-meridian-wednesday-17-may-2023-1.6847545?cmp=rss',0,null,0,0,null,0,0,0,0,'tday',0,0,0,null,0,0,0,0,null,null,null);
